## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The complexity of the relationship between language and culture means that interpretations can vary widely across different academic disciplines. Additionally, the examples provided are not exhaustive and may not represent all cultural contexts. Further research, including empirical studies and cross-cultural analyses, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.